snippet.title: 399 Perfects in 1 Race: Hatsune Miku: Roller Skating Music
snippet.description:
I had a pretty crazy race today while playing casual multiplayer. Hope you enjoy!

Hatsune Miku: Roller Skating Music is a brand new mobile Rhythm game. Right now it's not available in English but you should be able to understand the basics easily. 

Game Site : http://www.9game.cn/chuyinsu/
